Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.01,0:00:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.89,0:00:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從Mr.布朗的家回去後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終  什麼事也沒發生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁他們本來應該
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現在13日星期五的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說我發送的放棄跟蹤鈴羽的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變了世界線了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理也不會死  什麼事也不會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏的懷錶停掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪  明明剛剛才上過發條的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理…在兩小時後？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你重複著時間跳躍  無數次…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經歷了那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不好受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據阿萬音小姐所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們從現在所在的α世界線收束範圍移動到β世界線的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(343,325)\fscy80\fscx80}Attractor Field
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此  我們必須要使用IBN5100
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刪除掉SERN所掌握的關於你們的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  本應該在柳林神社的IBN5100
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界線發生移動的同時消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止所發送的D-Mail中造成世界線移動的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有六合彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐生小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漆原小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有跟蹤阿萬音小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取消掉最後的那條跟蹤阿萬音小姐的簡訊之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊延後了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  只要按相反順序取消掉所發送過的D-Mail的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能回到擁有IBN5100的原世界線中去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是假設
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何科學依據
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要存在可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是我提議的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要取消掉所有的D-Mail…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  工作量相當大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不得不做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的大腦是重要的樣本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算移動過世界線也能保持記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能忍受時間跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該測量一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我紅莉栖  我…會忘掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照順序的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個應該取消的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯的D-Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿至  菲伊莉斯在哪裡你應該心裡有數吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪  在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UPX會場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在雷Net的ABGC的決賽剛剛結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ABGC？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp0}雷Net Access Battlers Grand Championship的簡稱啊常考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本雷Net玩家齊聚一堂的大會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  現在以菲伊莉斯取得優勝結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯發送了D-Mail之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉原變了回原來的電器街
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚簡訊的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發送給誰了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發送了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  母貓跟一個穿白衣的男人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓他們跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  應該說他們跑不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我的黑暗力量手中  誰都跑不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在追你啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Viral Attackers喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Viral Attackers？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論使用何種卑鄙手段都要取勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不配玩雷Net的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為輸給了菲伊莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就來伏擊了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伏擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  剛才你好像給我打電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能告訴我D-Mail的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Mail？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發送給過去的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給過去的簡訊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條世界線上的菲伊莉斯並沒有D-Mail的記憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如  我說假如
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要是製作出了時間機器  你會相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真說是的話我就相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯也開發出了能移動到二次元世界的機器喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如  秋葉原是一個充滿了萌元素的街區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用時間機器  把它變成了像現在一樣的電器街
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會用什麼樣的方式？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼心理遊戲啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼  回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  充滿萌元素的街區很讓人開心喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  以前跟爸爸說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我在秋葉原開一家女僕咖啡店如何之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  遺憾的是被他拒絕了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是May  Queen嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你知道那個名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒告訴爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有的  May  Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這秋葉原
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉原本來就是一個充滿了萌元素的街區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比誰都愛這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為你所發送的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個街區都變樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底發送了什麼樣的簡訊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May  Queen本來應該在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要開的店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡工作過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿至是這裡的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是在這裡認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上菲伊莉斯杯白天部分就要開始了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰代號  G·B·A·C·K
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「世界有危險」來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天來了好多主人  好熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不取消D-Mail的話  會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理的性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你騙人喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是騙人的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏的性命有危險是怎麼回事喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了簡訊的內容了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不取消它不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理…真由理死了也無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓十年前死去的爸爸復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改變了爸爸會死去的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你斯文掃地了呢  小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  公主殿下  跟我們走一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我們抓到母貓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:55.67,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的那超危險的氣場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:59.81,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才開始就一直告訴我要把她染成黑色…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就見到那位大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那之前  我們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:03.93,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠站在第一線的永遠只有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:09.04,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是披著黑色羽毛的孔雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還打算繼續耍帥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  拜託你們住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  給我站住  你們都幹了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了啊  4℃大人參上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？怎麼了你們這幫傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？警察…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？逮捕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到聯繫說你獲勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕來為你慶祝  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會場裡找不到人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打手機也不接所以找了老半天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部君  該怎麼向你道謝才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道謝什麼的  不需要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我去觀看比賽的話說不定就不會發生這種事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  爸爸因為有工作所以也沒辦法喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留未穗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN5100?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  聽說您以前出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能取回呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了件對不起橋田女士的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋田女士…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是橋田鈴女士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她把IBN5100交給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒關係  一定會找到IBN5100的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:14:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴羽為我們拿到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  可以告訴他嗎喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命恩人很想知道啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前  留未穗曾經被綁架過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候公司規模還沒有現在這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿不出贖金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那時候出現了願意高價收購IBN5100的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就出手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧這樣才能湊齊了贖金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後  無論發生什麼我都會遵守和女兒之間的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是多麼微小的約定  也無論發生什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.76,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}畫上的字  左：爸爸  右：留未穗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓十年前死去的爸爸復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改變了爸爸會死去的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果取消D-Mail的話  那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫  你要發送D-Mail嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都會消失的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果不這麼做的話  真由理  你就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…剛才真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我非常的害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次感受到那麼多人的黑色感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來他們所有人都穿的一身黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我明明很認真地在說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能叫我「留未穗」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.19,0:00:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真  不  如果沒有岡部先生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道會發生什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別改口  和平時一樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  凶真  真是非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真呢  是我的王子殿下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是什麼王子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瘋狂的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏的性命有危險  是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是10年前  我8歲的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸約好了一起出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是由於工作原因去不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是沒辦法的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很寂寞  覺得爸爸其實並不愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著「爸爸什麼的不管了  乾脆死掉算了」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是和爸爸的最後一次交談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:17.57,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事故中確認死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.64,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}日本人…秋葉幸高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要改變那樣的過去  發了D-Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.47,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你女兒在我手裡  贖金1億  去坐新幹線
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是你父親就避開了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也沒有積極地將萌文化融入街區
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葉原就仍然是電器街嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸福啊  這10年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲…留未穗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發D-Mail吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸在10年前的事故中去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是真實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這10年只是一場夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他一起生活  也明白他是多麼愛我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏是我的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒法耍什麼性子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.19,0:00:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了世界線變化前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是變化後的事情也還記著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變化前和後的事情糾纏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要分不清哪邊才是真實了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還有什麼別的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  再找紅莉栖商量一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  不想給凶真添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為凶真是我的王子殿下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要從夢中醒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我只有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我稍微哭一會兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵喵  怎麼了喵  凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼精神哦喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.89,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}綁架是開玩笑的\N爸爸我愛你\N回頭見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界變回原狀之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的記憶就會全都消失嗎喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是擁有改變過去之前和之後兩邊的記憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯不想忘記和凶真一起度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動了  岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有看到菲伊莉斯的手機啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏也說不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就只有凶真了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵？喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真  你看了這裡面的「那個」嗎喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了的話就忘掉吧  那是必須封印的東西喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真  剛才那是應該吐槽的地方喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那個」是指什麼啊「那個」像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲伊莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙手算是什麼意思啊  那雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又打算做什麼變態的事情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫真大膽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真和菲伊莉斯在前世是與巨大的黑暗作鬥爭的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相愛的戀人喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係很親密的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.19,0:00:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和各種各樣的人戰鬥著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說菲伊莉斯小姐和岡部是同一類人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳林神社裡並沒有IBN5100
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前  菲伊莉斯確實把它供奉在了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到去年都還在這裡  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在哪裡


